text:
Your workplace can now find the perfect GIFs with Tenor thanks to you. Nice work! Two things:
1 - the safesearch setting for your workplace is PG and G. To change that, go here <https://slack.riffsy.com/TP2JMH5U3>.
2 - To share from a selection of GIFs, use `/tenor` plus a search term - `/tenor good job` for example.
Enjoy!
